# =====================================================================
#  智能猫窝 (Smart Cat-Care) — monorepo .gitignore
#  纳入：云端源码 / 前端源码 / 两块开发板完整 RT-Thread 工程(不含构建产物)
#  排除：密钥、数据库、AI模型、构建产物、工具链、依赖、备份、日志
#  注意：gitignore 的 # 只在行首才是注释，规则后不要写行尾注释！
# =====================================================================

# ---------- 通用 ----------
*.log
*.zip
*.tmp
.tmp/
.tmp-*
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.claude/
.idea/
.vscode/
.settings/
add_warnings.txt

# ---------- 顶层杂项 / 备份 / 过期副本 ----------
# 顶层 key_camera 为 4 月过期副本，board2 真身在 UDP/UDP/key_camera
/.compare-backup-20260521/
/.compare-backup-selected-20260521/
/.tmp-original/
/_backup_compare/
/key_camera/
/项目现状-2026-05-19.md
/board1-serial-*.log
/docs/superpowers/
xiaozhi-server/_git_server_backup/

# ---------- 工具链 / 二进制工具(README 说明从官方获取) ----------
/tools/openocd-5.16.1.4486-windows/
Edgi_Talk_M55_XiaoZhi_2/Edgi_Talk_M55_XiaoZhi/tools/

# ---------- 云端 xiaozhi-server ----------
# .env 含 DEEPSEEK_API_KEY，仅提交 .env.example
# models/ 是 848MB FunASR 语音模型，photos/ 是运行时上传照片
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.venv/
venv/
.pytest_cache/
.env
*.db
xiaozhi-server/models/
xiaozhi-server/photos/
xiaozhi-server/*.jpg
xiaozhi-server/*.wav

# ---------- 前端 xiaozhi-web ----------
node_modules/
dist/
*.tgz

# ---------- 嵌入式公共：RT-Thread 构建产物 ----------
build/
Debug/
*.elf
*.hex
*.bin
*.axf
*.map
*.o
*.obj
*.d
*.dep
*.lib
*.dblite
*.old
cconfig.h

# ModusToolbox IDE 生成的调试启动配置(超长路径/特殊字符，构建不需要)
*.launch
